PK\"/>\n*{{increase}} $5,872 ([[Purchasing power parity|PPP]], 2019 est.)<ref name=\"IMFWEOPK\"/>}}\n| per capita rank = {{plainlist| \n* [[List of countries by GDP (nominal) per capita|151st (nominal; 2019)]]\n* [[List of countries by GDP (PPP) per capita|132nd (PPP; 2019)]] }}\n| sectors = {{plainlist|\n*[[Primary sector of the economy|Agriculture]]: 18.5%\n*[[Secondary sector of the economy|Industry]]: 20.3%\n*[[Tertiary sector of the economy|Services]]: 61.2% (2019 est.) <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sbp.org.pk/ecodata/GDP_table.pdf |title=Gross Domestic Product of Pakistan (at constant basic prices of 2005-06) |work=SBP}} {{PD-notice}}</ref>}}\n| inflation = {{plainlist|\n*{{Increasenegative}} 14.56% (Jan 2020)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pbs.gov.pk/sites/default/files//price_statistics/monthly_price_indices/2019/cpi_review_october_2019.pdf|date=Oct 2019|title=Monthly Review on Price Indices|publisher=Pakistan Bureau of Statistics|accessdate=2019-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Pakistan annual inflation rate rises to 14.56% in January|url=https://in.reuters.com/article/pakistan-economy-inflation/pakistan-annual-inflation-rate-rises-to-14-56-in-january-idINKBN1ZV3UG|newspaper=Reuters|date=2020-02-01|accessdate=2020-02-06}}</ref>\n*3.925% (2018)<ref name=\"IMFWEOPK\"/>}}\n| bankrate = {{increase}} 13.25% (as on 16 July 2019)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1494422|title=State Bank raises benchmark interest rate to 13.25pc|date=2019-07-16|website=DAWN.COM|language=en|access-date=2019-11-16}}</ref>\n| poverty = {{plainlist|\n*34.7% on less than $3.20/day (2015)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/SI.POV.LMIC?locations=PK&name_desc=false |title=Poverty headcount ratio at $3.20 a day (2011 PPP) (% of population) |publisher=[[World Bank]] |website=data.worldbank.org |access-date=4 September 2019}}</ref>\n*{{steady}} 1.0% in [[extreme poverty]] {{nowrap| (September 2019)<ref name=\"World Poverty Clock\">{{cite web|url=https://wo