{"title_page": "1983 Bavarian Tennis Championships", "text_new": "{{TennisEventInfo|1983|Bavarian Tennis Championships|\n| date=16\u201322 May\n| edition=67th\n| draw=32S / 16D\n| prize_money=$75,000\n| surface=[[Clay court|Clay]] / outdoor\n| location=[[Munich]], West Germany\n| venue=MTTC Iphitos\n| champs={{flagicon|CSK}} [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]] <ref name=ms>{{cite web|title=1983 Munich Men's Singles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/en/scores/archive/munich/308/1983/draws?matchtype=singles|publisher=[[Association of Tennis Professionals]] (ATP)}}</ref>\n| champd={{flagicon|NZL}} [[Chris Lewis (tennis)|Chris Lewis]] / {{flagicon|CSK}} [[Pavel Slo\u017eil]] <ref name=md>{{cite web|title=1983 Munich Men's Doubles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/en/scores/archive/munich/308/1983/draws?matchType=doubles|publisher=[[Association of Tennis Professionals]] (ATP)}}</ref>\n| main_name=Bavarian International Tennis Championships{{!}}Bavarian Tennis Championships\n}}\n\nThe '''1983 Bavarian Tennis Championships''' was a men's [[Grand Prix tennis circuit]] tournament held in [[Munich]], [[West Germany]] which was played on outdoor [[clay court]]s. It was the 67th edition of the [[Bavarian International Tennis Championships|tournament]] and was held form 16 May through 22 May 1983. First-seeded [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]] won the singles title.<ref>{{cite web|title=ITF Tournamentdetails|url=http://www.itftennis.com/procircuit/tournaments/men's-tournament/info.aspx?tournamentid=1010002879|publisher=ITF}}</ref>\n\n==Finals==\n\n===Singles===\n{{main|1983 Bavarian Tennis Championships \u2013 Singles}}\n{{flagicon|CSK}} [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]] defeated {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Joakim Nystr\u00f6m]] 6\u20130, 6\u20133, 4\u20136, 2\u20136, 7\u20135\n* It was \u0160mid's 5th title of the year and the 26th of his career.\n\n===Doubles===\n{{main|1983 Bavarian Tennis Championships \u2013 Doubles}}\n{{flagicon|NZL}} [[Chris Lewis (tennis)|Chris Lewis]] / {{flagicon|CSK}} [[Pavel Slo\u017eil]] defeated {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Anders J\u00e4rryd]] / {{flagicon|CSK}} [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]] 6\u20134, 6\u20132\n* It was Lewis's 2nd title of the year and the 9th of his career. It was Slozil's 4th title of the year and the 15th of his career.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.atpworldtour.com/Tennis/Tournaments/Munich.aspx ATP Tournament profile]\n* [http://www.bmwopen.de Official website]\n\n{{BMW Open tournaments}}\n{{1983 Volvo Grand Prix}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1983 Bmw Open}}\n[[Category:1983 BMW Open| ]]\n[[Category:Bavarian International Tennis Championships]]\n[[Category:1983 in tennis|Nabisco Grand Prix]]\n[[Category:May 1983 sports events in Europe]]\n", "text_old": "{{TennisEventInfo|1983|Bavarian Tennis Championships|\n| date=16\u201322 May\n| edition=67th\n| draw=32S / 16D\n| prize_money=$75,000\n| surface=[[Clay court|Clay]] / outdoor\n| location=[[Munich]], West Germany\n| venue=MTTC Iphitos\n| champs={{flagicon|CSK}} [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]] <ref name=ms>{{cite web|title=1983 Munich Men's Singles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/en/scores/archive/munich/308/1983/draws?matchtype=singles|publisher=[[Association of Tennis Professionals]] (ATP)}}</ref>\n| champd={{flagicon|NZL}} [[Chris Lewis (tennis)|Chris Lewis]] / {{flagicon|CSK}} [[Pavel Slo\u017eil]] <ref name=md>{{cite web|title=1983 Munich Men's Doubles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/en/scores/archive/munich/308/1983/draws?matchType=doubles|publisher=[[Association of Tennis Professionals]] (ATP)}}</ref>\n| main_name=Bavarian International Tennis Championships{{!}}Bavarian Tennis Championships\n}}\n\nThe '''1983 [[Bavarian International Tennis Championships|Bavarian Tennis Championships]]''' was a men's [[Grand Prix tennis circuit]] tournament held in [[Munich]], [[West Germany]] which was played on outdoor [[clay court]]s. It was the 67th edition of the tournament and was held form 16 May through 22 May 1983. First-seeded [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]] won the singles title.<ref>{{cite web|title=ITF Tournamentdetails|url=http://www.itftennis.com/procircuit/tournaments/men's-tournament/info.aspx?tournamentid=1010002879|publisher=ITF}}</ref>\n\n==Finals==\n\n===Singles===\n{{main|1983 Bavarian Tennis Championships \u2013 Singles}}\n{{flagicon|CSK}} [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]] defeated {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Joakim Nystr\u00f6m]] 6\u20130, 6\u20133, 4\u20136, 2\u20136, 7\u20135\n* It was \u0160mid's 5th title of the year and the 26th of his career.\n\n===Doubles===\n{{main|1983 Bavarian Tennis Championships \u2013 Doubles}}\n{{flagicon|NZL}} [[Chris Lewis (tennis)|Chris Lewis]] / {{flagicon|CSK}} [[Pavel Slo\u017eil]] defeated {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Anders J\u00e4rryd]] / {{flagicon|CSK}} [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]] 6\u20134, 6\u20132\n* It was Lewis's 2nd title of the year and the 9th of his career. It was Slozil's 4th title of the year and the 15th of his career.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.atpworldtour.com/Tennis/Tournaments/Munich.aspx ATP Tournament profile]\n* [http://www.bmwopen.de Official website]\n\n{{BMW Open tournaments}}\n{{1983 Volvo Grand Prix}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1983 Bmw Open}}\n[[Category:1983 BMW Open| ]]\n[[Category:Bavarian International Tennis Championships]]\n[[Category:1983 in tennis|Nabisco Grand Prix]]\n[[Category:May 1983 sports events in Europe]]\n", "name_user": "Wolbo", "label": "safe", "comment": "Moved wikilink", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1983_Bavarian_Tennis_Championships"}
